{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, and he sat on top of me practically until the policeman came, from the ghetto, to pick us up, to escort us back to-- to the ghetto, which happened almost like 45 minutes later.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He sat on top of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I thought I'll suffocate, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to beg him, please, move off my chest, because I can't breathe anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And why did he scream?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he was afraid that, if they will go back two instead of three of us, that they will hold them responsible for the fact that an [INAUDIBLE]-- To the ghetto that nigh?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--escaped.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't think this was the case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wouldn't hold responsible anybody for anything, for the simple reason that they couldn't care less.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ghetto was controlled by the Jewish cops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no-- I mean the Germans hardly paid attention at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Except that-- unless there was something going to happen, like a deportation, a liquidation, a round-up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is when the Germans would-- would come in and staff their own people and put guards around it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, at that point, there was nobody there, really, as far as I know, as far as I could tell.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But still, he wanted to play it safe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't want to take a risk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Therefore, he risked my life instead of taking a chance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So this is how they foiled my escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Lech stood-- stood there for the longest time, until he left or something went wrong, and he took off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Good for him that he took off.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
